<h2>üìç Scenario 1: House Party</h2>

<div class="scenario-box">
It's Friday night, and you're at an off-campus house party with about 30-40 people. Music is loud, people are drinking and dancing.

You notice someone who appears very intoxicated - unsteady on their feet, slurred speech - being led upstairs by someone they seem to have just met. 

Your friends are nearby in the living room, chatting and laughing.
</div>

